724930f-a.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 92nd Street (East)
724930f-a.text:
York Ave., at East 92nd Street. The new East River Drive, is a con-
tinuation of this Ave., north of 92nd Street.
March 29, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

724931f-b.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 92nd Street (East)
724931f-b.text:
(1)
York Ave., north from Nast 92nd to 93rd Streets. This Ave. will
extend northward along the East River, to form the new East River Drive.
On the right, appears a portion of the Municipal Ferry to Astoria, L.I.
October 9, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, another view.
September 20, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
